  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 12 informal schools with local volunteers</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nairobi&apos;s informal schools face formidable challenges with class sizes commonly reaching 80. In our work in local schools over the last 6 years it has become clear to us that they need support to reduce class sizes and improve the quality of education. Our network of over 100 volunteers is eager to help the community and gain skills and experience. We will co-ordinate placing volunteers in 12 informal schools where they are needed most and support targeted mentoring of the most vulnerable pupils</narrative>
  </description>
